flowchart TB
    SIG["Signal Received<br/>SIGINT / SIGTERM"]
    P1["Phase 1: Drain<br/>Stop accepting new work"]
    P2["Phase 2: Cancel<br/>Signal all tasks to stop"]
    P3["Phase 3: Grace Period<br/>Wait for in-flight completion"]
    P4["Phase 4: Force Exit<br/>Drop everything, terminate"]

    SIG --> P1
    P1 --> P2
    P2 --> P3
    P3 --> P4

    style SIG fill:#c0392b,color:#fff,font-size:16px
    style P1 fill:#d4a017,color:#fff,font-size:16px
    style P2 fill:#d4a017,color:#fff,font-size:16px
    style P3 fill:#2d8a4e,color:#fff,font-size:16px
    style P4 fill:#2c3e50,color:#fff,font-size:16px
